{"tid":116580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TRUMP確認《日美安保條約》適用於尖閣諸島","createTime":"2017-02-11T13:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T12:56:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23a0549aa2069b0b414b29bd9b9202ac2d83a601","tid":116580,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1313037-20170211.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1313037-20170211.htm&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=11748bc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1313037-20170211.htm&h=7d90c153\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1313037-20170211.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1313037_1_L_20170211211831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1313037_1_L_20170211211831.jpg&h=dfa58ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在白宮與到訪的日本首相安倍晉三會談後，兩人一同見記者。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普形容日本是美國相當重要的盟友，承諾推動美日關係更緊密，合作促進航海自由，共同應對北韓威脅。他又強調，美國會致力確保日本的安全，包括所有屬於日本行政管理的地區。<br />\n<br />\n安倍表示，日美確認尖閣諸島屬於《日美安保條約》第5條的適用對象，美國會加強在區內部署。對於特朗普政府退出跨太平洋夥伴關係協定，安倍表示充分瞭解特朗普的決定，日本將與美國建立新的貿易關係。"},{"pid":"ec5ea398cc3a9bc791347aa7549a36790ef37388","tid":116580,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"激死支那"},{"pid":"7e8e618152a9456c385b3bb91e2e791d33d99b15","tid":116580,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"痴撚線總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c2e17485940be321ef4875612769d5c64b4de1","tid":116580,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有乜地方痴線呢請問？"},{"pid":"fae5700575e96962580f9d6716668294933d90ce","tid":116580,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱先認同一中 轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ae1c34051def4a49969002b54198078faabcca","tid":116580,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱先認同一中 轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：特朗普給習近平承認一個中國政策，代價是中國默許釣魚台的主權屬於日本，美軍的協防將伸延至釣魚台列島一帶。<br />\n特朗普摸熟了與中共做交易的方法了。先威脅取走中國的大東西（一個中國的政策），然後將這個大東西交還給中國，之後便可以安然取走一些小東西。這大概是人類與猴群做的交易了。"},{"pid":"b33cad1d939530b86b711b55ccfd06d5e18b7342","tid":116580,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"The greatest president ever<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cce0c77b100bfee146e9b07800edaa893da862","tid":116580,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>The greatest president ever<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fdcbb8d22e4f487f8f6d1eee0cb47dc3208908","tid":116580,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1795eb413657322cf8f48bede206f8140eb619a","tid":116580,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱先認同一中 轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：特朗普給習近平承認一個中國政策，代價是<span style=\"color: red;\">中國默許釣魚台的主權屬於日本</span>，