d3396aac5cc58ce3b1","tid":116580,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱先認同一中 轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇返美國個新聞稿，係話尊重美國自身既一中政策，唔係中國既一中政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以美國龍門點搬都得，係班傻鳩中國佬係報紙打哂飛機"},{"pid":"1194b0344803984558e2f70b92492c7c4c798aca","tid":116580,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:47:06.000Z","msg":"2014年04月23日<br />\n奧巴馬：美日安保條約適用於釣魚台<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20140423/52407908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20140423%2F52407908&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9b29f98b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20140423%2F52407908&h=d11817f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20140423/52407908</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e1511a50bbdecc119ddc22b7bd1ac0cc6aacc2","tid":116580,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱先認同一中 轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇返美國個新聞稿，係話尊重美國自身既一中政策，唔係中國既一中政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以美國龍門點搬都得，係班傻鳩中國佬係報紙打哂飛機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講句, 就算美國真係尊重一中又點<br />\n根本台灣唔係中國統治, 就算美國尊唔尊重, 都係一樣嫁啦<br />\n唔通美國話尊重一中, 就會第二日將台灣送比中國咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果中共係有膽, 有實力......就直接出兵攻佔台灣, 並且擊退美軍<br />\n到時就算美國支持台灣獨立都無用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共成日係到嘈, 叫人尊重一中, 根本好撚搞笑<br />\n<br />\n因為對方尊唔尊重, 都對現實無影響"},{"pid":"bbfffe3ae084eef810d95f584eb271ea94c41455","tid":116580,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2014年04月23日<br />\n奧巴馬：美日安保條約適用於釣魚台<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20140423/52407908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20140423%2F52407908&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9b29f98b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20140423%2F52407908&h=d11817f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20140423/52407908</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬 果一次只係口頭承諾<br />\n今次係「確認」<br />\n<br />\n不過其實 美國政府 就算唔確認<br />\n都肯定會出兵幫日本"},{"pid":"4c29efc769c04fa25912541d3f84d9585b4a8eb9","tid":116580,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q4o6d10m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq4o6d10m&h=b29892ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08884d07c4818e74678d73f6aaa9efa87be6f992","tid":116580,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啱啱先認同一中 轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好明顯台灣仲未俾甜頭侵侵,咁侵侵咪口頭認同一中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n安倍去美國應該帶左唔少合約過去過大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n安保第五條其實只係重彈奧巴馬既老調<br />\n如果安倍咁樣都只係得呢個&quot;保證&quot;其實都幾蝕水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實中國都無膽出兵<br />\n就算中國真係出兵........以日本既能力, 都可以打敗中國<br />\n所以日本真係唔需要呢個保證<br />\n<br />\n如果我係安倍, 我一定霸氣咁講:「感謝美國朋友支持, 但如果中國真的來攻, 我日本足矣應付, 無需美國朋友出手」"},{"pid":"f83b74386e46bc654bd155fdb57b86d5aa99b3aa","tid":116580,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:58:25.000Z","msg":"雜種係唔係腳震緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b920b73aa1fa48ee93f44775a810717e15a0bb1","tid":116580,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱先認同一中 轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：特朗普給習近平承認一個中國政策，代價是中國默許釣魚台的主權屬於日本，美軍的協防將伸延至釣魚台列島一帶。<br />\n特朗普摸熟了與中共做交易的方法了。先威脅取走中國的大東西（一個中國的政策），然後將這個大東西交還給中國，之後便可以安然取走一些小東西。這大概是人類與猴群做的交易了。</blockquote><br />\n侵侵幾時承認中國的&quot;一個中國原則&quot;？<br />\n侵侵係話會尊重美國自已&quot;一個中國政策&quot;"},{"pid":"910c9595ed54364f41ee41b51383d6666b26b40b","tid":116580,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雜種係唔係腳震緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反正中共都知自己唔會開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n家陣習總叫人民日報繼續出幾篇新聞屌下美國,日本, 比班大陸人打下J<br />\n跟住就番上床屌女屌到腳震"}]}